<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hagenau, Colmar, Schlettstadt, Weißenburg, Oberehnheim, Kaysersberg, Mühlhausen, Turckheim und Rosheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass König Sigismund noch zu Brünn weilt und die Hussiten Kuttenberg und umliegende Städte eingenommen haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="138v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l18"><expan>Meıſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd Reͣten des <expan>Heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Reıchs Stette in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l19">Elſeſſen Nemlıch Hagnaw Colmar Slettſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l20"><expan>Weıſſenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / Obern Ehenheim Keyſerſperg / <expan>Mülhawſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l21">Türinkeim vnd Roſheım . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſunderlıebe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l23"><expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıg / vnd ob wır ıcht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l24">meͣre weſten etwas <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> etc / Das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l25">Vnd tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu wıſſen / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> dıe nehſt <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l26">wır von dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l27">gehabt haben / do ıſt ſein <expan>künıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade / dennoch ʒu Prünn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l28"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / des xıııȷ <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyn / vnd ſeıd haben wır niht </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_280" id="139r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l1"><expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre von ſeinen <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / ſo wıſſen wır auch ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l2">dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſuſt nıht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre . wan daʒ dıe Huſſen den Perg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l3">ʒum Kutten vnd etwıeuıl ſtette daſelbſumb vor etlıchen <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l4"><expan>eıngenome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ynnenhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> / als eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> / auch wol mag <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l5">haben / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_280_r1l6"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Vrbanj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="138v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Meist<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und reͣten des
                                                  <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> reichs stette in
                                                Elsessen, nemlich Hagnaw, Colmar, Slettstat,
                                                  <expan>Weissenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, Obern
                                                Ehenheim, Keysersperg,
                                                  <expan>Mülhaws<ex>en</ex></expan>, Türinkeim und
                                                Rosheim, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>besunderliebe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. künig und, ob
            wir icht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> meͣre westen, etwas <expan>zu
              v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan> etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
            und tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu wissen, die nehst
              <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die wir von dem
              <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig gehabt haben,
            do ist sein <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade dennoch zu Prünn
                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, des xiiii <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> seyn; und
            seid haben wir niht <pb facs="#facs_280" id="139r"/>
<expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre von seinen <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. So wissen wir auch zu disen
              <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> sust niht <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre,
            wan daz die Hussen den Perg zum Kutten und etwievil stette daselbsumb vor etlichen
                <expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>laid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eingenome<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>ynnenhabe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ewr
                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> auch wol mag
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> haben. Denn wo wir
              <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Urbani.</ab>
</div>
